{"tid":1425742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"OL兼Model孫凱怡斥示威者搞事自私：香港依家經濟繁榮","createTime":"2019-08-06T20:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:39:46.000Z","uid":12558,"like":1,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"9c26382f7c02f2b37bf5e77944510feac2833d26","tid":1425742,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:12:54.000Z","msg":"香港特區政府擬修訂逃犯條例而惹起大批市民的不滿，引發了連串的反修例行動，包括大型的遊行、示威和抗議等，並向政府提出了五大訴求，不過特首林鄭月娥至今仍未回應，令到爭取政府回應訴求的市民、多個團體以及工會於昨日（5日）參與罷工行動，藉此來向政府施壓。而昨日的罷工以及連串不合作行動引起了交通大混亂，路面道路多處出現堵塞情況，港鐵多條線的服務更一度癱瘓，導致要上班的市民受到影響。一位自稱在中環任職OL的Model孫凱怡 (Penny) 對此大表不滿。<br />\n<br />\nPenny除了在中環做OL，其實她還有從事Freelance model的工作，之前也有出席過品牌的公開活動，報道曾以藝人來稱呼她。昨日Penny於荔景站接受《香港01》直播的訪問時，就斥責進行不合作運動阻塞港鐵的示威者阻住她以及一班市民返工，表示：「我覺得好過分，完全唔諗人感受，係好自私嘅行為。政府係有做得唔好嘅地方，但係我覺得 (示威者) 唔需要做到咁囉。依家咁阻住，可能要去探病或者睇醫生 (嘅人) 咁點呢？有無諗過其他人接唔接受你 (示威者) 咁做？其實只係少部分人咁做咋喎。」<br />\n<br />\nPenny自言並不清楚昨日會有示威者堵塞地鐵，又多次強調示威者的不合作運動好自私，她說：「我唔知可以點做，佢哋有無幫我哋諗下可以點做？」她又力撐香港政府表示：「政府依家做咗啲咩咁嚴重呢？我覺得依家經濟繁榮，嚟緊會有好大嘅問題咁邊個去負責？個個都失業咁點呢？你返屋企堵塞唔好畀你父母返工先啦，你點解要阻住其他市民？呢個行為好過分囉。」其實Penny之前亦有於她的facebook出post指責示威者破壞公物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3124671/org/ebb546a71ed9e6cebe9ee78881252284.jpg/LuECp9e6sE83r0Sw3HSOP_G025YMyNCBLYb0Zi2G9GY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3124671%2Forg%2Febb546a71ed9e6cebe9ee78881252284.jpg%2FLuECp9e6sE83r0Sw3HSOP_G025YMyNCBLYb0Zi2G9GY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e49cb8dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3124746/org/bfe0bcc2b12c153b24dddb3475b99371.jpg/IBedP82iWdKdrixVOsdbfz3Tc2gfQ_NFZrY4Kma2OCo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3124746%2Forg%2Fbfe0bcc2b12c153b24dddb3475b99371.jpg%2FIBedP82iWdKdrixVOsdbfz3Tc2gfQ_NFZrY4Kma2OCo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c6f057df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3124800/org/a44fecbbd9f25006c943f72d2c66765d.jpg/q1uoEK4a9gC2DeTeZ4V8AG5xocInpv6dsuiPY7Loj2M?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3124800%2Forg%2Fa44fecbbd9f25006c943f72d2c66765d.jpg%2Fq1uoEK4a9gC2DeTeZ4V8AG5xocInpv6dsuiPY7Loj2M%3Fv%3Dw480&h=fd835020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3124802/org/7deec5329836ba17bb8ced83cfd71634.jpg/Q9EAm0yQVBUhbm0RQGiR7JKrDzDiCzmWvlEglL5RIJQ?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3124802%2Forg%2F7deec5329836ba17bb8ced83cfd71634.jpg%2FQ9EAm0yQVBUhbm0RQGiR7JKrDzDiCzmWvlEglL5RIJQ%3Fv%3Dw480&h=7ef7789b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3124794/org/893e442bb683f85f0925f35706630947.jpg/01Uk37RVyH9uKzr2CPvFUS5BWgKfEgqh5iwQz-YsEM8?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3124794%2Forg%2F893e442bb683f85f0925f35706630947.jpg%2F01Uk37RVyH9uKzr2CPvFUS5BWgKfEgqh5iwQz-YsEM8%3Fv%3Dw480&h=0d92a85a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04dabdec8df5d0c5db03f03e6eb5a43708bd2a8b","tid":1425742,"uid":135503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061111f4209c2fbc568509d8875632a53e52024d","tid":1425742,"uid":82829,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:14:55.000Z","msg":"Dont make stupid ppl famous"},{"pid":"4ef0c452659582bd63f2aa9f8a88093cfd1a1eed","tid":1425742,"uid":29283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:15:20.000Z","msg":"好撚樣 唔好推"},{"pid":"f02e96ac83f92462ae74eda56044a7ee9a3ad4ed","tid":1425742,"uid":34334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5aa626e65c22c458992396a018ace313029d4f7e","tid":1425742,"uid":29283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":